member.name: CABINET_INFO
member.summary: TheCABINET_INFO structure stores information about a cabinet file. The function specifies this structure as a parameter when it sends aSPFILENOTIFY_NEEDNEWCABINET notification to the cabinet callback routine.

member.name: CABINET_INFO.DiskName
member.summary: Name of the source media that contains the cabinet file.

member.name: CABINET_INFO.SetId
member.summary: Identifier of the current set. This number is generated by the software that builds the cabinet.

member.name: CABINET_INFO.CabinetNumber
member.summary: Number of the cabinet. This number is generated by the software that builds the cabinet and is generally a zero- or 1-based index indicating the ordinal of the position of the cabinet within a set.
